						               													<description>Dogs of War is a game of Modern Mercenary Actions and Adventure. The player assumes the role of a Commander of a special group of Mercenaries available for hire by corporations and governments to complete hazardous missions. As the Commander, you must accept dangerous missions and assemble your Mercenaries in order to successfully resolve the missions.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;GAME OBJECTIVE&amp;#10;The objective of Dogs of War is to successfully complete a number of missions in order to gain the highest profit, as determined by Resource Points (RP), for your outfit. The player can choose to play a short game (4 Missions), an average game (6 Missions) or a long game (8 Missions). Once all Missions have been resolved (successfully or not) the Player totals his RP earned and compares this with the Commander&amp;rsquo;s Profit Table to determine the level of success.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Game features Units with stunning graphics that include MERC Teams, Militia, Government Troops, PBRs, Hueys, MI-17s, Alouette Helicopters, Hind Gunships, Leaders, Tanks, AFVs, Mortars, Artillery and Airstrikes.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Mission Actions and Combat are resolved on a tactical level.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
